name: PregnancyFoodGuide
0:
”Alexa, Open Pregnancy Food Guide”
”Is it safe to drink coffee while pregnant?”
”Can I eat peanuts during pregnancy?”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: pregnancy food guide
des:
Pregnancy Food Guide contains information on more than 1500 kinds of food and drink. It will give you easy access to crucial food safety information during your pregnancy so you can feel confident about the food and drink choices you're making. 

The voice interface allows you to easily access the information where ever you are in your daily routine. Use it in the kitchen while preparing food and refer to the visual cues in the Alexa app for easy reference on previous searches.

This tool does not provide medical advice, and is for informational and educational purposes only, and is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment or diagnosis. Call your doctor to receive medical advice. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
